OOC: I finally figured out how to do this.  I'm combining reviving him 
with something else I wanted to do.

Cutie is in a fog of energy between our world and the Matrix watching 
????? and waiting.  Suddenly a voice comes from the Matrix.

Matrix:  Cutie it is time to become one great warrior.

Cutie: NO I NEED MORE TIME!  IT CAN'T END LIKE THIS! I CAN'T LOOSE TO 
MY FINAL OPPONENT!  THE MARK OF A TRUELY GREAT WARRIOR IS NOT HOW MANY 
BATTLES HE HAS WON, BUT DID HE WIN HIS FINAL ONE AND I DID NOT!  I 
MUST DEFEAT THE EVIL BOT!

Matrix:  Cutie you cannot do more than you can.  You must join now.

Tentacles of light reach out for him, but Cutie begins to fight.  
Somehow he pulls the fog and it begins to swirl around his spark (his 
psyical body isn't here like before) and get pulled in like a 
whirlpool.
